h.k . bank to rais prime rate soon , dealer say bank in hong kong are like to rais prime rate by half a percentag point to 6-1/2 pct follow a one-quart point prime rate increas by two major u.s. bank yesterday , dealer said . they told reuter local bank may decid on the increas at thi weekend 's routin meet of the hong kong associ of bank . g.c . goh , chief dealer of the standard charter bank , said prime rate increas by citibank and chase manhattan bank to 7-3/4 pct from 7-1/2 may prompt hong kong bank to follow suit . goh said local bank want to restor the prime to 6-1/2 pct , the level at begin of 1987. the bank rais the prime to the current six pct from five pct on februari 28 after cut it 1-1/2 point from 6-1/2 on januari 15 in respons to upsid pressur on the hong kong dollar , he said . the medium and longer term interbank rate firm today , with three month end at 5-1/16 to 4-7/8 pct against yesterday 's five to 4-13/16 close . the overnight rate , howev , fell to 3-1/2 to three pct from 4-1/2 to four becaus of increas liquid for a local stock issu .